Text.string: Come on, come on, COME ON!
This'll be just for the craic!
Let's have a chat, shall we?
Better leave before ya get hurt.
You lookin' to act the maggot?
There you are, you big ugly, you.
A dose of Zane'll do ya, biggun.
Look't the size of this one!
Naught but a bigger arse to boot!
Was lookin' for a good fight!
A bigger mug to bloody my knuckles.
Well, you're a pint-and-a-half, ain't ya?
Thought I was through surprising myself!
Look out, world! I'm even better now.
And the world quaked in terror! [laughs]
Really turned a page! [afterthought] That was a thing once. “Books.”
Get that attractive bastard right there!
That dashin' fook over there was makin' eyes at your sister!
Get the new guy! [under breath] Idiots.
That's a good lookin' bullet sponge!
Hot DAMN! You look good, Zane-boy.
Jealous the rest of ya get to see this all the time.
[light panic] I'm the fake! I'm the fake!
[false voice] Look, it's the REAL Zane! There!
Go on, be distracting, will ya?
Take a look at me little friend.
Paint the town red! With blood, in case that wasn't clear.
You got a job to do.
Show me what you've got, little bud!
This should cover my arse for a bit.
Personal space! Need some personal space!
Just need something between me and your breath.
Don't worry, you can still look at me.
Nothing like cover when you're getting shot at!
There's a rich vein of dumbass, right over there!
Kill anything you find over there!
Secure that area! It's full of idiots!
Better run before my little buddy gets ya!
That party's over and you're the bouncer!
I want that spot cleared out!
Ah, that was a lucky shot.
I'm gonna get you for that.
This ain't looking good for me.
Shoe's untied, back in a moment!
Is that a shiny penny down there?
Oh, Zane-boy, this is not a good look for you.
Ah! Never doubted me for a second!
Not the fifty-first time I faked my death! [afterthought] Don't look into it.
This was my plan all along!
Ha, and you thought I'd go out like that.
Knew you'd fall for that old trick!
Death, ya feckless runt, you haven't caught me yet!
Ha! Knew I could do it.
Can't keep a good man down! Or me.
High five, decoy! Oops, you're gone.
I can always count on myself to get me out of a pinch.
I got all kinds of tricks!
I was the prettier one anyway.
Gotta get back to the fight!
It'll go better this time. Definitely probably.
That wasn't according to plan. Not that I had a plan.
Oi, someone point me at the nearest bastard to shoot.
Rough night. Let's have another one!
I played poker with the devil. Anyway, I'm back -- and now I can play the saxophone.
It ain't a proper bloodbath without Zane!
Just stopped back in town for a pint!
Back and lookin' better than ever somehow.
Hoo. Let's never do that again.
I'd call this a successful operation.
It's possible you picked the wrong battle.
Got more where that came from!
Got any more for the meat-grinder?
Are you seein' this? Open your bloody eyes!
Deathbringer is also my middle name.
I'm on FIRE! But not literally.
Naught but a bushel of manky gits.
Your parents should be ashamed of ya.
Didn't anyone teach you how to fight?
Trigger finger's gettin' tired over here.
And bullets for YOU, and bullets for YOU -- EVERYBODY gets bullets!
Thought I took care of that a while ago.
Sorry I'm late -- there was a thing with drunken spiderant and a princess, and... ach, it's a whole thing. Let's get to it.
Oh, what a mighty Vault Hunter! Also, you're here.
Come on, boyos! Let's show 'em how to dance!
Health here! Not that I need it.
If you sad lot need some healing, it's over here.
You're lookin' a bit worse for wear. Come get this.
Any o' you's need some healin'?
Not a pint, but it'll do.
I'll go ahead and take that.
Does a body good. My body, specifically.
Ohh, what a shiny lovely you are.
You are looking so very fine.
[excited drooling over a fancy thing noises] Oh hoo-hoo, goodness yes.
What an exquisite little fella you are.
You're as pretty as a paycheck.
[sarcastic] No, no. It's all right. I'll just stay here pullin' my pud.
Oi! We gonna get movin' soon or what?
These boots were made for walkin', not standin'.
I look better in motion. Let's move.
What are we standin' around fer? There's lootin' and shootin' to do!
I'd rather be runnin' and gunnin'.
(sigh) Everybody needs a break sometimes, I guess.
Who's runnin' this operation? We're wasting time here!
Oh god, I can't feel my arse! I can't feel my arse!
Big money, big money, big money!
This is my favorite part. Except for all the other parts.
Show me what we're workin' with!
A new haul. Let's see here.
Come on, let's have a go!
I wouldn't fight me if I was you.
Let's test the cut of your giblets.
Let's have a nice clean fight! Ah, I'm just kidding. Dirtier the better!
All right then. It's your funeral.
Hope you got a casket on layaway.
Tell my boy the reaper to treat you kindly.
Bad idea for you, but I'll bite.
Knew I shoulda carb-loaded this mornin'!
Oh, I didn't realize your mum was callin' the fight!
Claptrap paid me to take a dive.
I made a fortune betting against me.
I'll get you next time. And the one after that. [quieter] And the one after that.
I took it easy on you.
Tie? Never had one of those.
How do you know you're better'n people when you tie?
You bought the ref off, didn't cha?
I'm far too humble to brag about how badly I beat your arse.
Don't worry. Only everyone saw it.
Me father always said I throw a mean punch.
What, no applause? Do I have to do everything myself? [claps]
Ah, refreshing! Like an iceberg slip-'n'-slide in your birthday suit!
Thought we'd go higher than that!
You got a pilot's license, boyo?!
Oh, it's that kind of a ride, is it?
Looks like we're takin' the scenic route!
Ah, so you can read my mind!
I'm knackered. Someone else want to drive?
I could do with a snoozer.
Let Papa Zane teach you how to drive, boyo.
My arse is fallin' asleep, let's switch.
(tearfully) Me brother would be so proud.
(tearfully) My sister always loved a good explosion!
We're a sixer and a sausage short of a cookout!
That's a bad way to go.
Not lookin' too pretty down there!
Whoops, didn't see you there! [quieter] I totally saw him there.
Didn't you hear the horn?! [quieter] I didn't hit the horn.
Outta the way! -- oops, too late.
Almost feel bad about that. Almost.
You were supposed to get out the way!
Chipped the paint. (beat) And everything else.
We probably didn't need that part.
Do we... exchange information now, or...?
May need to make a jump for it!
We're smokin'! And I ain't talkin' about the meat!
I'm about to start roastin' me chestnuts over here.
This seems less than entirely safe.
I'd rather not die in a flaming wreck.
This would be a bad way to go!
Are you TRYING to get us killed?
Where did you learn to drive?
Did a skag teach you how to drive?
This isn't looking good for us!
Anyone admiring my goods while I'm admiring my goods?
Let's see... which one looks like more fun?
Numbers, numbers... where's the number for fun factor?
I've got a hell of a lot of good stuff here.
All right then. Where the hell are we going?
What a lovely map we've got here.
Let's see, if I'm here... and I'm heading...
Look at the adorable little icons.
So many skills, so little time.
What kind of badass do I wanna be today?
It's so hard to choose a favorite gadget.
I love ALL my gadgets, though!
Death doesn't hurt, but that -- (gurgling death rattle)
At least I'll leave... a beautiful corpse.
Never again! For real this time!
Oi, Reaper! I'm coming for ya, you bastard.
All men die. But a rare few die looking this feckin' good.
Someone better write me a hell of a drinking song!
Sing songs about me, or I'll haunt the crap out of ya!
To be honest... I can't believe I survived this long.
Death comes for us all. But you first.
They'll be singing songs about that one.
A new chapter in me saga!
You couldn't hit a cow's arse with a banjo.
This can't be how you saw this going.
Well look at the state o' you.
Don't say I didn't warn ya!
That wasn't so hard now, was it?
End of the road for ya!
Ferocity's my middle name. Zane Ferocity Flynt.
Sharpshooter's my middle name. Zane Sharpshooter Flynt!
Got a bit of a boo-boo there.
Yeah, I'm pretty good at this.
Hope you weren't fond of that face.
Lookin' a little worse for wear, m'friend.
I'm too fast and you're too dead.
I'm in this for the fun of it. And that was fun.
What's black and blue and red and full of bullets?! [sotto voce] It's you.
Glad I kept some gadgets around.
Not so big and bad now, are ya?
Aw, he thought he was tough.
Only room for one-to-four badasses 'round here!
Not lookin' so badass NOW, are ya?
Tell the reaper he still owes me a fiver.
The bigger they are... the more fun it is to shoot 'em in the friggin' face!
Someone was gonna send you on yer way.
Looks like yer in a bit of a state.
Went a bit arseways for ya.
Say hello to the great beyond for me.
Looks like you could use a pick-me-up.
I'll need ya later, I will.
Here, it's good for what ails ya.
One for you, one for me.
Two shorten the road, back on your feet.
Not exactly lookin' to get ended today!
Ooof, I'm good. I'm getting there.
All righty now, back on me boots.
I owe you one. (beat) How many's that make now?
[to self] Come on, Zane-boy. Up you go.
I'll take you from arse up to arse down in no time.
That would have been embarrassing for you.
Go on! And pull your socks up, mate.
Ah, you'd do it for me too, you would.
Yeah, yeah, back to the fight with ya.
Get your mitts offa my ride!
Keep all yer limbs outside the vehicle at all times!
See what we've got over there.
Keep on eye on that brute.
Should we get that one then?
More storage? Always a good thing.
Didn't think I COULD look better. Wonders never cease.
Could someone please come appreciate this?
How good do I look? Go on. Don't hold back.
I'm far too humble to say how great I look right now.
New threads, new look, new me.
Might as well do it with some style.
Anyone else seein' this? Mmm, mm, mm.
Only one thing to say about that. Hell yeah!
Oh, Zane, you're lookin' bad! But good-bad. Not bad-bad.
Think I got the better of that one.
Forgot to study my crazy-arse-alien jibberish.
This makin' sense to anyone else?
Think I missed this class in school.
Look at me, I'm the driver now.
I'm commandeering this vehicle! And by that I mean I'm stealin it!
I need this more than you.
I was just about to get up meself, but, uh... thanks.
I owe you a pint, boyo.
I mean, I had it covered. (beat) Okay, no I didn't.
I knew you couldn't live without me.
Couldn'ta done it without you. Probably.
Ah, feels good to be back.
Can I get back to the killin' now?
Think I got the better end of this.
Hard to turn down good gear!
An operative's only as good as his tools. And mine are bloody incredible!
Shoulda known better than to let a Siren grab ya!
Like shootin' fish in a crazy ghost hand.
You're just linin' them up for me!
I wanna see what's in there.
Someone's left a perfectly good chest out!
Got a bead on a chest.
We're on a proper tear here!
We come out on top, as usual!
Baddest bastards in town, we are!
Ha, thought I was gonna throw a grenade, did ya?
I'll be back for you later.
Not ready yet. Huh, never said that before.
Just you wait, I'll be back!
Oh, I'll get you soon enough.
Think I can make sense of this now.
I'm surprised I can't handle that.
Guess I'm too rusty for that one.
I'll come back for you later.
I guess I still need that.
I chuck that after I'm done with it.
Ah! I swear I'm good for it.
Do you take kidneys as payment? I've got a few.
Thinkin' I can crack it now.
Guess I'll give it a whack.
Nothin' doin' on this bad boy.
What am I supposed to do with this?
Doesn't seem to be working yet.
Where do we need to be goin'?
Never seen a bad picture of me.
I got nothing but good sides here.
Make sure you get the mesmerizing light in me eyes.
Careful, don't get lost in my eyes.
How do I look? Just kiddin'! I know I look fantastic.
Pictures of me are illegal on a few planets. Just so you know.
Cheese! (beat) Ohhhh, I could go for some of that right now.
Need some blood. Running on empty!
I could use a pint. Of blood.
I'm barely holding me guts in here!
I'm dying over here! Does anyone care that I'm dying over here?!
(pained) Okay -- gotta admit, that one hurt.
Ain't doin anyone any good down here!
If I die, take the credit. I got three dozen bounties on me head.
